 133:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_spi.c ****        Using the HAL it is not possible to reach all supported SPI frequency with the different SPI
 134:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_spi.c ****        the following table resume the max SPI frequency reached with data size 8bits/16bits,
 135:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_spi.c ****          according to frequency of the APBx Peripheral Clock (fPCLK) used by the SPI instance.
